{
  "stem": "22869.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because, any second, you're dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they took the rifles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were shooting, you know, in the air and hitting you with the butt of the rifles, and creating such a chaos that-- that was-- that was-- I mean, it's hard to describe, what it-- what it did to you.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It just-- you-- you fell in line, whether you wanted to or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I-- and I, looking backwards, today, I think that all that thing was like manipulation to try to keep you in a fear in such a manner that you should not get the idea of running away.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the very early stages, the worst fear of the Germans-- I mean, I've known that from literature that I read, that I know was that, God forbid, the outside world should find out of what's going on in the inside world of concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They kept it a secret.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's-- it-- it was-- they did not want-- don't forget, we're talking about '42-- the world should find out on what they're doing there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a selection there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I-- everybody passed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, like I said, we were still in the early stages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us in to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because this train was arriving in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All trains arrived-- all transports arrived in Birkenau, not in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We just-- we just saw-- I mean, I later on found out that Mengele was Mengele.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't know Mengele.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he was going around and just looking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we saw, I would say, quasi able-bodied young people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were 1,500 of us, at that time, with this transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the youngest probably was about 16, and the oldest was mostly 35.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
